watchdog: wm831x_wdt: use devm_gpio_request_one()

Use devm_gpio_request_one() to make cleanup paths simpler.
Also, GPIOF_DIR_OUT | GPIOF_INIT_LOW is replaced with
GPIOF_OUT_INIT_LOW.

